"title": "1090: God, majesty of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1090: god, majesty of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The greatness and splendour of God, revealed in his creation and mighty works of deliverance. On account of his majesty, God is worthy of praise and adoration from all people.</p>\n<h2>God is majestic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:1\">HEB 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:29\">1SA 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:10\">PSA 24:10</a> <em>The word translated “glory” also means “majesty”</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3-Heb1:4\">HEB 1:3–1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Majesty belongs to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11\">1CH 29:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:12\">PSA 145:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:25\">JUD 1:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's majesty is awesome</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:22\">JOB 37:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:10\">ISA 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:19\">ISA 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:21\">ISA 2:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's character is majestic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1\">PSA 93:1</a></strong> <em>A figurative expression indicating that God is fully majestic.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:11\">EXO 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1\">PSA 104:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:5\">PSA 145:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:14\">ISA 24:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:10\">ISA 26:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's activity is majestic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:6-Exod15:7\">EXO 15:6–15:7</a></strong> <em>“hand” is a symbol of God's power which accomplishes his purposes.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:26\">DEU 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:2-Deut11:3\">DEU 11:2–11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:6\">2CH 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:3\">PSA 111:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:43\">LUK 9:43</a></p>\n<h2>God's name is majestic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1\">PSA 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:9\">PSA 8:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's voice is majestic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:4\">PSA 29:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:4\">JOB 37:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:30\">ISA 30:30</a></p>\n<h2>God's presence is majestic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:27\">1CH 16:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:6\">PSA 96:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:9\">2TH 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h2>The risen Christ shares in God's majesty</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16-2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:16–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3-Heb1:4\">HEB 1:3–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:1\">HEB 8:1</a></p>\n<h2>God's delegated majesty</h2>\n<h3>To the Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:4\">MIC 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>To kings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:5\">PSA 21:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:3-Ps45:4\">PSA 45:3–45:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:2-Ps110:3\">PSA 110:2–110:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's majesty provides help for his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:34-Ps68:35\">PSA 68:34–68:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:6\">EXO 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:26-Deut33:27\">DEU 33:26–33:27</a></p>\n<h2>Experiences of God's majesty</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:4\">ISA 6:1–6:4</a> <em>Isaiah's vision</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:4-Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:4–1:28</a> <em>Ezekiel's vision</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:3-Hab3:6\">HAB 3:3–3:6</a> <em>Habakkuk's description of God's person and work</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:1-Rev4:11\">REV 4:1–4:11</a> <em>John's vision</em></p>\n<h2>Human responses to the majesty of God</h2>\n<h3>An awareness of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>An awareness of insignificance</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:15\">ISA 40:15</a></p>\n<h3>Worship and adoration of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:1-Ps92:8\">PSA 92:1–92:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1\">PSA 93:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:3-Ps95:6\">PSA 95:3–95:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46\">LUK 1:46</a></p>",
